# Project Structure Guide

This is an Astro-based landing page project with multiple campaign variations. Each campaign has its own dedicated directory structure.

## Core Structure

- **[src/pages/](mdc:src/pages)** - Campaign landing pages, each in its own directory
- **[src/components/](mdc:src/components)** - Reusable Astro components
- **[src/layouts/](mdc:src/layouts)** - Page layout templates
- **[package.json](mdc:package.json)** - Project dependencies and scripts
- **[astro.config.mjs](mdc:astro.config.mjs)** - Astro configuration

## Campaign Structure Pattern

Each campaign follows this pattern (example: KRT20711):
- **[src/pages/KRT20711/index.astro](mdc:src/pages/KRT20711/index.astro)** - Main landing page
- **[src/pages/KRT20711/static/](mdc:src/pages/KRT20711/static)** - Campaign-specific assets
  - `css/` - Stylesheets
  - `picture/` - Images and graphics
  - `image/` - Additional image assets

## Key Components

- **[src/components/RedirectCode.astro](mdc:src/components/RedirectCode.astro)** - Redirect handling
- **[src/components/BaseHead.astro](mdc:src/components/BaseHead.astro)** - HTML head template
- **[src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro](mdc:src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro)** - Base page layout

## Development Commands

- `bun dev` - Start development server
- `bun build` - Build for production
- `bun preview` - Preview production build
